80
00:08:54,532 --> 00:08:55,464
<i>Don't die...</i>

81
00:08:56,534 --> 00:08:57,501
<i>Don't die!</i>

82
00:08:58,436 --> 00:08:59,596
<i>Don't die!</i>

83
00:09:00,404 --> 00:09:01,598
<i>Don't die!</i>

84
00:09:02,373 --> 00:09:03,499
<i>Don't die!</i>

85
00:09:12,516 --> 00:09:13,813
The bet...

86
00:09:21,859 --> 00:09:22,951
I won it.

87
00:09:26,197 --> 00:09:28,028
I-It's impossible...

88
00:09:39,543 --> 00:09:44,845
Hokage is... my dream, eh?

89
00:09:56,127 --> 00:09:57,151
<i>For the last time...</i>

90
00:09:59,897 --> 00:10:01,228
<i>For the last time...</i>

91
