That's not what I meant.

97
00:10:37,268 --> 00:10:38,200
What?

98
00:10:38,869 --> 00:10:44,466
Your battle is with me,
there's no time to look away.

99
00:10:45,242 --> 00:10:48,643
<i>Who would have imagined this?</i>

100
00:10:49,280 --> 00:10:52,408
<i>If that child is found by the Akatsuki,</i>
<i>there will be trouble.</i>

101
00:10:53,317 --> 00:10:55,410
