Hokage some day...

119
00:13:26,437 --> 00:13:28,837
What utter nonsense...

120
00:13:29,741 --> 00:13:33,074
By the way...
to hell with Hokage!

121
00:13:33,811 --> 00:13:36,006
Only a fool does that job.

122
00:13:37,782 --> 00:13:41,582
<i>To hell with Hokage!</i>
<i>Only a fool does that job.</i>

123
00:13:48,726 --> 00:13:50,057
<i>The wishes of the two...</i>

124
00:13:51,028 --> 00:13:55,055
<i>More importantly, Lady Tsunade,</i>
<i>your wish...</i>

125
00:13:56,100 --> 00:13:57,727
<i>Have you forgotten your dream?</i>

126
00:14:03,341 --> 00:14:05,434
<i>The successive lines of Hokage</i>
<i>have protected</i>

127
00:14:05,510 --> 00:14:08,843
<i>the Leaf Village and</i>
<i>and those living in it.</i>

128
00:14:09,147 --> 00:14:12,913
<i>They brought troubled times under control</i>
<i>and helped the village to prosper.</i>

129
00:14:12,984 --> 00:14:15,748
<i>They risked their lives</i>
<i>for this dream, this ideal!</i>

130
00:14:20,558 --> 00:14:24,221
<i>Anyone who makes fun of the old man</i>
<i>and the Fourth Hokage...</i>

131
00:14:24,295 --> 00:14:26,593
<i>It doesn't matter if</i>
<i>you are a woman!</i>

132
00:14:26,964 --> 00:14:28,932
<i>I'll clobber you with all my might!</i>

133
00:14:39,577 --> 00:14:44,139
And now,
I also will put my life on the line!

134
00:14:47,685 --> 00:14:51,712
If your life is worth throwing away
for a kid like him...!

135
00:14:52,290 --> 00:14:55,555
Then dying now would be
a fitting end!

136
00:15:15,146 --> 00:15:17,944
All that's left... is Naruto.

137
00:15:18,916 --> 00:15:19,974
Lady Tsunade!

138
00:15:23,621 --> 00:15:24,781
<i>Make it in time!</i>

139
00:15:37,001 --> 00:15:40,300
<i>She's still able to move even</i>
<i>after I pierced her down to her lungs!</i>

140
00:15:49,514 --> 00:15:52,449
You mean you'll still protect that kid?!

141
00:15:56,287 --> 00:15:57,720
That's what I said...

142
00:15:58,389 --> 00:15:59,447
From now...

143
00:16:01,959 --> 00:16:04,018
I'm putting my life on the line!

144
00:16:05,596 --> 00:16:07,530
You, half dead corpse!

145
00:16:21,279 --> 00:16:26,216
No matter how cool you try to be,
your trembling doesn't stop.

146
00:16:26,918 --> 00:16:30,684
You can't get away from
the curse of hemophobia.

147
00:16:31,822 --> 00:16:37,624
And yet, why would you
take the blows for that kid?

148
00:16:38,296 --> 00:16:42,232
Why would you battle for the Leaf?

149
00:16:53,411 --> 00:16:54,309
<i>No way!</i>

150
00:16:54,845 --> 00:16:56,676
<i>Tsunade's trembling has...</i>

151
00:16:57,315 --> 00:16:58,339
<i>has stopped?</i>

152
00:17:00,384 --> 00:17:03,114
That is because... I am...

153
00:17:07,758 --> 00:17:11,558
the Leaf Village's... Fifth Hokage!

154
00:17:13,130 --> 00:17:14,154
That sign is?!

155
00:17:16,000 --> 00:17:18,195
<i>Lady Tsunade has conquered</i>
<i>her fear of blood,</i>

156
00:17:18,269 --> 00:17:19,566
<i>but that's...</i>

157
00:17:23,608 --> 00:17:26,168
What are you saying you'll do,
after all this time?

158
00:17:26,844 --> 00:17:33,272
You can't fight with that wound
even if you've conquered your fear.

159
00:17:38,356 --> 00:17:44,920
W-Wait! I'll treat that wound.
So don't release that seal!

160
00:17:48,132 --> 00:17:49,793
<i>Release the Secret Seal!</i>

161
00:17:50,334 --> 00:17:53,565
<i>Ninja Art. Mitotic Regeneration!</i>

162
00:18:09,987 --> 00:18:11,545
<i>What is this Jutsu...?!</i>

163
00:18:16,694 --> 00:18:21,427
It looks like I'm not the only one
who develops new Jutsu.

164
00:18:21,966 --> 00:18:25,060
What in the world is this Jutsu?

165
00:18:25,670 --> 00:18:26,602
Well...

166
00:18:27,705 --> 00:18:31,436
For many years I've stored Chakra
in my forehead.

167
00:18:32,710 --> 00:18:36,771
The mass of Chakra stimulated
a variety of proteins.

168
00:18:37,114 --> 00:18:40,379
The number of times my cells divide
speeds to a dizzying rate...

169
00:18:41,052 --> 00:18:42,713
The cells rebuild...

170
00:18:43,454 --> 00:18:47,652
and all the organs and body systems
are revitalized.

171
00:18:48,292 --> 00:18:51,523
It's not the ability to restore,
it's the ability to reincarnate.

172
00:18:52,163 --> 00:18:55,690
That means I won't die... from battles.

173
00:18:58,102 --> 00:19:02,266
<i>But the number of times a person's cells</i>
<i>divide in their lifetime is fixed...</i>

174
00:19:02,707 --> 00:19:07,508
<i>If that is sped up,</i>
<i>it essentially shortens the life!</i>

175
00:19:10,514 --> 00:19:11,640
Lady Tsunade!

176
00:19:13,350 --> 00:19:14,339
<i>That action is...</i>

177
00:19:15,186 --> 00:19:16,619
Lord Orochimaru!

178
00:19:19,423 --> 00:19:20,913
<i>Come out!</i>

179
00:19:22,626 --> 00:19:23,684
Hurry!

180
00:19:24,995 --> 00:19:26,895
Ino, inu, saru, tori, hitsuji!

181
00:19:29,467 --> 00:19:30,957
- Summoning Jutsu!
- Summoning Jutsu!

182
00:21:06,164 --> 00:21:10,863
<i>I believe your promise,</i>
<i>its a true heart give me courage</i>

183
00:21:10,935 --> 00:21:15,269
<i>Always I feel it</i>
<i>the precious time with you</i>

184
00:21:15,873 --> 00:21:19,400
<i>On your still shoulder</i>

185
00:21:20,645 --> 00:21:25,105
<i>I feel the wind that blows</i>
<i>towards tomorrow</i>

186
00:21:25,283 --> 00:21:30,721
<i>The city lights are like pieces of stars</i>

187
00:21:31,222 --> 00:21:35,522
<i>That hold us together</i>

188
00:21:35,993 --> 00:21:45,231
<i>"Each one of us glows differently,"</i>

189
00:21:45,303 --> 00:21:47,897
<i>you say laughingly</i>

190
00:21:48,139 --> 00:21:53,805
<i>but you look most dazzling</i>

191
00:21:54,378 --> 00:21:58,747
<i>Like a comet,</i>

192
00:21:58,816 --> 00:22:04,914
<i>like the rainbow after the storm</i>

193
00:22:04,989 --> 00:22:12,088
<i>You bring light into my heart</i>

194
00:22:13,097 --> 00:22:22,472
<i>Being lost can be the answer</i>

195
00:22:23,808 --> 00:22:31,340
<i>Let's promise we won't cheat</i>

196
00:22:31,415 --> 00:22:35,408
<i>Uh...like a shooting star,</i>
<i>we do go ahead.</i>

197
00:22:38,322 --> 00:22:42,622
The time to conclude this long, fateful
confrontation has come, Orochimaru.

198
00:22:42,960 --> 00:22:45,326
You have sunk too deeply into vice.

199
00:22:45,563 --> 00:22:47,861
You are no longer a comrade!

200
00:22:48,132 --> 00:22:51,693
Comrade? How odious.

201
00:22:51,836 --> 00:22:54,270
That word makes me shiver.

202
00:22:54,639 --> 00:22:56,607
I will bring you down!

203
00:22:56,674 --> 00:23:00,110
Today is the last day that
we are called Sannin!

204
00:23:00,444 --> 00:23:02,776
Next time:
"Deadlock! Sannin Showdown!"
